text: "Breakfast in America" is a 1979 song by English rock band Supertramp and is the title track to their sixth studio album of the same name. It went to the top ten in Ireland, the United Kingdom and South Africa. It went to number 62 in the United States and did not chart in Australia and New Zealand. ==References== Category:1979 songs Category:Progressive rock songs Category:Supertramp songs
